  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN341">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>vēntu kuṟaiyuṟavuṅ koṭāa ṉēntukōṭ</l>
<l>ṭampūn toṭalai yaṇittaḻai yalkul</l>
<l>cempoṟic cilampi ṉiḷaiyō ṭantai</l>
<l>yeḻuviṭ  ṭamaitta tiṇṇilaik katavi</l>
<l>ṉaraima ṇiñci nāṭkoṭi nuṭaṅkum</l>
<l>.................................................................</l>
<l>pulikkaṇat taṉṉa kaṭuṅkaṭ cuṟṟamoṭu</l>
<l>māṟṟa māṟāṉ maṟaliya ciṉattaṉ</l>
<l>pūkkō ḷeṉavēeyk kayampuk kaṉaṉē</l>
<l>viḷaṅkiḻaip polinta vēḷā melliyaṟ</l>
<l>cuṇaṅkaṇi vaṉamulai yavaḷoṭu nāḷai</l>
<l>maṇampuku vaika lākuta loṉṟō</l>
<l>vārama ruḻakkiya maṟaṅkiḷar muṉpi</l>
<l>nīḷilai yeḵka maṟutta vuṭampoṭu</l>
<l>vārā vulakam pukuta loṉṟeṉap</l>
<l>paṭaitoṭ ṭaṉaṉē kuruci lāyiṭaik</l>
<l>kaḷiṟuporak kalaṅkiya taṇkayam pōlap</l>
<l>peruṅkavi ṉiḻappatu kollō</l>
<l>meṉpula vaippiṉit taṇpaṇai yūrē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Even though a king makes a request he won’t give [her],</l>
<l>the father of the young one, [her] anklets with refined markings,</l>
<l>[her] hips with foliage as a decoration in a skirt of pretty flowers, with eminent curves.</l>
<l>Banners sway daily on the ramparts half of earth</l>
<l>with doors in firm condition fixed by letting go cross bars.</l>
<l>………………</l>
<l>Along with [his] fierce-eyed retinue, like a pack of tigers,</l>
<l>the angry man who gives fight, not one who changes [his] reply,</l>
<l>has entered the ? pond as for the flower giving [ceremony].</l>
<l>[Pondering] “tomorrow being the day of entering into union</l>
<l>with her of beautiful breasts adorned with beauty spots,</l>
<l>of soft nature who is willing(?), flourishing with shining jewels, is one thing</l>
<l>[and] one thing is entering the world that is coming </l>
<l>with a body cut up by a long leaf[-shaped] blade?”</l>
<l>the lord touched [his] weapon. In between these [two],</l>
<l>like a cool pondy stirred up when an elephant thrashes about</l>
<l>will it lose [its] great beauty,</l>
<l>the village in the cool fields in a region of soft soil?</l>
</lg>
